 {"id":"bd-ehk.7","title":"Unit tests: Bloodstream delta propagation correctness","description":"Unit tests: Single row change propagates to exactly the bound widgets. Multi-row batch delta propagates atomically. Unbound tables produce no deltas. Schema change triggers full re-render (not partial delta). LOGGING SPEC: Assert bloodstream.delta span with correct rows_changed and widgets_invalidated. Assert no stale data visible during propagation.","status":"open","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-02-13T18:03:08.802301376Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-02-13T18:03:08.802301376Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["bloodstream","cross-crate","test","unit"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-ehk.7","depends_on_id":"bd-ehk","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-02-13T18:22:56Z","created_by":"import","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
 {"id":"bd-ehk.8","title":"Unit tests: franken_trace schema compatibility matrix","description":"Unit tests: Serialize trace with schema version N, deserialize with version N reader (pass). Serialize with version N+1, deserialize with version N reader (graceful failure with migration error). Evidence record roundtrip serialization. LOGGING SPEC: Assert trace.compat_check span. Assert ERROR log for incompatible versions.","status":"open","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-02-13T18:03:08.937567441Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-02-13T18:03:08.937567441Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["cross-crate","schema-compat","test","unit"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-ehk.8","depends_on_id":"bd-ehk","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-02-13T18:22:56Z","created_by":"import","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
 {"id":"bd-ehk.9","title":"E2E test: Bloodstream database-to-terminal round-trip","description":"End-to-end test: (1) Insert rows into FrankenSQLite materialized view, (2) Verify FrankenTUI table widget updates without polling, (3) Measure propagation latency (target: sub-millisecond for single row), (4) Verify O(delta) time (10 rows changed should not re-render 10K unchanged rows). LOGGING SPEC: Assert full span chain: sql.insert -> bloodstream.delta -> incremental.recompute -> widget.render. Assert bloodstream_propagation_duration_us histogram. Assert no full-table re-render.","status":"open","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-02-13T18:03:09.062074963Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-02-13T18:03:09.062074963Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["bloodstream","cross-crate","e2e","test"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-ehk.9","depends_on_id":"bd-ehk","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-02-13T18:22:56Z","created_by":"import","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
